Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.26,0:00:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛\N{\fs38}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盯着我干嘛\N{\fs38}Why are you looking at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.98,0:00:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想出去么\N{\fs38}You want to go outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.36,0:00:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想出去吗\N{\fs38}Outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.55,0:00:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不想啊\N{\fs38}Outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.54,0:00:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑 靠\N{\fs38}Are you kidding me?! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.27,0:00:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fs38}Oh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.21,0:00:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs38}W-what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.98,0:00:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的蠢狗\N{\fs38}Your idiot dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:01:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是故意的 爸\N{\fs38}Oh, he he didn't mean it, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.63,0:01:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 嗅嗅 好孩子\N{\fs38}D-did you, Snuffles? You're a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先别表扬他 Morty\N{\fs38}Don't praise him now, Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.73,0:01:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他刚尿在地毯上了\N{\fs38}He just peed on the carpet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.53,0:01:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坏狗狗\N{\fs38}Bad dog! Bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.86,0:01:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 快来 我今晚要你帮忙\N{\fs38}Morty, come on. I need your help tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 Rick\N{\fs38}Hey, wait, hold on a second, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会碰巧有什么能让这狗\N{\fs38}You wouldn't by any chance have some sort of crazy science thing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.87,0:01:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更聪明的科学发明吧\N{\fs38}You could whip up that might help make this dog a little smarter, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,养狗的目的不就是为了有优越感吗 Jerry\N{\fs38}I thought the whole point of having a dog was to feel superior, Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.96,0:01:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是你 就不会想做这事\N{\fs38}If I were you, I wouldn't pull that thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.45,0:01:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走 Morty\N{\fs38}Come on, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.01,0:01:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 要是你想继续在这儿白住\N{\fs38}Listen, Rick, if you're gonna stay here rent-free
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.62,0:01:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉我儿子帮你搞啥破科学 至少你\N{\fs38}And use my son for your stupid science, the least you could do
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.93,0:01:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要帮这家里做点事吧\N{\fs38}Is put a little bit of it to use for the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不把狗弄聪明点\N{\fs38}You make that dog smart or...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.81,0:01:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就禁足Morty\N{\fs38}Morty's grounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 不要\N{\fs38}Aw, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你真是让我别无他法了 Jerry\N{\fs38}Boy, you really got me up against a wall this time, Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 皱皱\N{\fs38}All right, Ruffles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫啥来着\N{\fs38}What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.69,0:01:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗅嗅\N{\fs38}Snuffles.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.47,0:01:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗅嗅 握手\N{\fs38}Snuffles, shake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打滚\N{\fs38}Roll over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去上厕所\N{\fs38}Go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.95,0:01:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 妈啦  - 我的天\N{\fs38}- Holy crap! - No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.33,0:01:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下你满意了吧 Jerry\N{\fs38}Yeah, you're at the top of your game now, Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.33,0:01:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩得开心\N{\fs38}Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:01:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走 Morty\N{\fs38}Come on, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.71,0:02:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太神奇啦 Rick\N{\fs38}That was fantastic, Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你喜欢那玩意儿的话\N{\fs38}Yeah, morty, if you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.32,0:02:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个一定能让你大吃一惊\N{\fs38}boy, you're you're really going to flip your lid over this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.28,0:02:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是啥\N{\fs38}W-w-w-what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.83,0:02:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 只要把这个设备\N{\fs38}It's a device, Morty,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放进你的耳朵里 就能进入别人的梦里\N{\fs38}That when you put it in your ear, you can enter people's dreams, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟你老说的那电影一样\N{\fs38}It's just like that movie that you keep crowing about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,<盗梦空间>吗\N{\fs38}You talking about "Inception"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 Morty\N{\fs38}That's right, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那个差不多 但是这个不扯\N{\fs38}This is gonna be a lot like that, except, you know, it's gonna maybe make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,<盗梦空间>也不扯好吗\N{\fs38}"Inception" Made sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用跟我说这些 Morty\N{\fs38}You don't have to try to impress me, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我们去你数学老师Goldfold先生家\N{\fs38}Listen, tonight we're gonna go into the home of your math teacher, Mr. Goldenfold, and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将你数学得A的想法植入他脑子里\N{\fs38}We're g we're gonna incept the idea in his brain to give you a's in math, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你就\N{\fs38}That way you can, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就能天天帮我搞科学了\N{\fs38}Y-you're gonna help me with my science, Morty, all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 你花时间在搞这种发明\N{\fs38}Geez, Rick, in the time it took you to make this thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能直接帮我把作业做了吗\N{\fs38}couldn't you have just, you know, helped me with my homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有好好听我说的话吗\N{\fs38}Are you listening to me, morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作业有害智商 少做才是正解\N{\fs38}Homework is stupid. The whole point is to get less of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.58,0:02:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走 我们快过去把事情办了\N{\fs38}J-j come on, let j let's just get over there and deal with this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你老师的梦里\N{\fs38}W-we're gonna incept your teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说扫兴话了\N{\fs38}Y-y-y-y-y-you're frustrating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本不认识我\N{\fs38}You don't know me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 Pancakes太太 好极了啊\N{\fs38}Nice, Mrs. Pancakes real nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:03:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一周的<Pancakes太太的日日夜夜>\N{\fs38}Next week on "The days and nights of Mrs. Pancakes"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本不认识我\N{\fs38}You don't know me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他妈就让我好好地认识认识你\N{\fs38}Then let me get to know yo, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 剧透\N{\fs38}Uh-oh! Spoilers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我落了一季没看呢\N{\fs38}I'm a full season behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 我们居然就这么跑到我老师的房子里来了\N{\fs38}Wow, Rick, I can't believe we're sitting around, standing around in Mr. Goldenfold's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太诡异了\N{\fs38}It's really weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就会更诡异了 Morty\N{\fs38}It's about to get a whole lot weirder, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦脆片 麦脆片\N{\fs38}Wheat thins. Wheat thins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我来两份\N{\fs38}I'll take two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你吃得够多了 先生\N{\fs38}Oh, I think you've had enough, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又不认识我\N{\fs38}You don't know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 Morty 是时候动手了\N{\fs38}All right, Morty, time to make our move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弹一弹\N{\fs38}Make it bounce.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀\N{\fs38}No, you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抖一抖\N{\fs38}Oh, jiggle it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手了啦\N{\fs38}You better stop with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真主至上\N{\fs38}Allahu akbar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这飞机是我们的了\N{\fs38}We're gonna take control of this plane!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不给Morty Smith更好的数学成绩 我们就重演911\N{\fs38}We're gonna 9/11 it unless Morty Smith gets better grades in math!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 说了不许动\N{\fs38}Hey! I said nobody move, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不叫"嘿"\N{\fs38}The name's not buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫Goldenfold\N{\fs38}It's Goldenfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃我麦脆片\N{\fs38}Nice to wheat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找掩护 Morty\N{\fs38}Take cover, Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:03:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗷\N{\fs38}Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没想到Goldenfold这么厉害\N{\fs38}Goldenfold's got more control here than I anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这人不是高中数学老师吗\N{\fs38}I mean, the guy teaches high-school math.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到他在梦里这么有主动权\N{\fs38}I-I-I-I didn't take him for an active dreamer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得干掉他让他醒过来\N{\fs38}We got to take him out so he wakes up, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们不能死\N{\fs38}But we can't get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你在别人梦里被杀掉 你就真的死了\N{\fs38}If you get killed in someone else's dream, you die for real, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥 你说啥\N{\fs38}What?! Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怂什么\N{\fs38}Don't be a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现实生活中不是躲过不少子弹吗\N{\fs38}You avoid getting shot in real life all the time, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这儿也一样躲 不就没事了\N{\fs38}Just do the same thing here, and we'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我把拖鞋拿来\N{\fs38}Now bring me my slippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗅嗅 来帮我垫脚\N{\fs38}Now, be my footstool, snuffles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才对嘛\N{\fs38}This is what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才叫狗狗\N{\fs38}This is a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯哼 这样挺好的\N{\fs38}Oh, yeah. This should play out just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们婚礼上你就说了这句话 连讽刺的语气都一样\N{\fs38}You said the same thing, equally sarcastically, at our wedding
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.09,0:04:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果呢\N{\fs38}and guess what.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 他想和我们说话\N{\fs38}Oh, my god. He's trying to tell us something.
