Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.37,0:17:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阶段二开始\N{\fs38}Begin phase two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗军占领东部沿海 战争仍在继续\N{\fs38}Fighting continues as the dog army captures the Eastern seaboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显然人类统治的纪元将迎来了苦涩的终结\N{\fs38}It appears clear at this time that the era of human superiority has come to a bitter end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你别杀我\N{\fs38}Please! Please don't kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在说什么 Bill\N{\fs38}What's she saying, Bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.37,0:17:28.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得她在说"我爱千层面"\N{\fs38}I think she's saying, "I love lasagna."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38\an8}human testicles 人睾丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 Fido\N{\fs38}Thank you, Fido.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.03,0:17:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 我以为你死了\N{\fs38}Rick! I thought you were dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.99,0:17:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不 我只是装死\N{\fs38}No, no, no, I was just playing dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:17:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好消息\N{\fs38}Good news, though, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:17:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切马上就要结束了\N{\fs38}This whole thing's gonna be over really soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:17:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥\N{\fs38}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:18:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个梦 Morty\N{\fs38}It's a dream, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在你的狗的梦里\N{\fs38}We're in your dog's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗抓住我们的那天晚上\N{\fs38}The night the dogs captured us,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你吓哭了 拉在了裤子里 然后我们都睡着了\N{\fs38}after you cried and crapped your pants, we... we all went to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我用梦境植入装置把我们两个弄进了嗅嗅的梦里\N{\fs38}Then I used my dream inceptors to put the two of us inside snuffles' dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.91,0:18:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这都过了差不多一年了\N{\fs38}But I-it's been like a whole year!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是六个小时\N{\fs38}It's been six hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦里的时间是现实时间的一百分之一\N{\fs38}Dreams move one one-hundredth the speed of reality, and dog
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而狗的时间是人的七分之一\N{\fs38}Time is one-seventh human time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里过一天 外面一分钟\N{\fs38}So, you know, every day here is like a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就和<盗梦空间>一样 把人搞得很晕 而且很蠢\N{\fs38}It's like "Inception," Morty, so if it's confusing and stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.22,0:18:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这部人人爱的电影就这个样\N{\fs38}then so is everyone's favorite movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我很喜欢这样的生活呀\N{\fs38}Aw, man. I really liked this life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过至少我没有真的拉在裤子里吧\N{\fs38}Well, at least I didn't really crap my pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这事儿是真的 在你睡着之前就拉了\N{\fs38}No, no, that happened before you went to sleep, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在就睡在你的屎里呢\N{\fs38}You're sleeping in your crap right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.93,0:18:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一一件确确实实发生了的事\N{\fs38}Out of all the things that happened to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你拉在裤子里了\N{\fs38} that was the only real thing that, you know, is that you crapped your pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.68,0:18:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直一团糟\N{\fs38}I mean, it's a mess out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有些沾到我手上了\N{\fs38}I got some on my hands, Morty,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我给弄到梦境植入器上了 还有一坨掉进了我的嘴里\N{\fs38}And then I got it on the dream inceptor, and a piece fell in my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 不是吧\N{\fs38}Aw, man, geez! Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.01,0:18:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管了 Morty\N{\fs38}Look, d-d-d-don't worry about it, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来把这个吃了\N{\fs38}Here, here take these, Morty. Take these.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些药能让我醒过来还是怎么的\N{\fs38}Are these pills supposed to wake me up, or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多吧\N{\fs38}Close.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个会让你的肾功能停止\N{\fs38}It's gonna make your kidneys shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥\N{\fs38}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为了我们的计划 Morty\N{\fs38}It's necessary for the plan, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.93,0:18:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心 哥们儿\N{\fs38}Don't even trip, dawg.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况很糟 雪球陛下\N{\fs38}It's pretty bad, Emperor Snowball.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还需要做一次手术\N{\fs38}We're gonna need to do another operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜一切\N{\fs38}Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜一切代价救回我的宝贝Morty \N{\fs38}Anything for my precious Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为您的会计师 我必须告诉您\N{\fs38}Sir, as your accountant, I must advise you that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些医疗支出会让您的财政到达岌岌可危的地步\N{\fs38}these medical expenses are putting you in serious financial jeopardy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.30,0:19:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您可能会失去您的帝国\N{\fs38}You could lose your kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.89,0:19:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去他的帝国 斤斤计较的会计\N{\fs38}To hell with my kingdom, bean counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意牺牲这一切 来换得这个人类的健康和幸福\N{\fs38}I would trade it all for my human's health and happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得他们会为我们做到这一步吗\N{\fs38}Do you think they would have done this for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们又不是他们\N{\fs38}We are not them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是 他们\N{\fs38}We are not... them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召集军队\N{\fs38}Assemble the troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了一个决定\N{\fs38}I've made a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.27,0:19:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占领人类世界\N{\fs38}Taking over the human's world
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会造成更多的残忍与伤痛\N{\fs38}will lead to nothing but more heartbreak, more cruelty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们决定去新世界建立一个智慧狗类的社会\N{\fs38}Instead, we will go to a new world and colonize it with a society of intelligent dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.89,0:19:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会再犯人类的错误\N{\fs38}One that will not make the same mistakes as humanity
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.12,0:19:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且会有强制宠物保险\N{\fs38}and one where pet insurance will be mandatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会想你的 雪球\N{\fs38}I'm gonna miss you, Snowball.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.94,0:20:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以叫我嗅嗅 Morty\N{\fs38}You can call me Snuffles, Morty
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会想你的 非常想念\N{\fs38}and I'm going to miss you, too, very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.28,0:20:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry\N{\fs38}Jerry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs38}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.22,0:20:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就和<老黄狗>的结局一样\N{\fs38}It's just like the end of "Old Yeller."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么说是因为里面也有狗吧\N{\fs38}Oh, Jerry. You mean because it had dogs in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个智慧狗类居住的世界\N{\fs38}Wow! A whole world populated by intelligent dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想知道会是什么样啊 Rick\N{\fs38}I wonder what it'll be like, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得肯定很棒 Morty\N{\fs38}I think it will be great, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.71,0:20:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以发展成一个\N{\fs38}You know, it's g I-I-I-I-it could be developed in-into
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好的全年龄向节目啊\N{\fs38}a very satisfying project for people of all ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.01,0:20:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每一集至少愿意看十一分钟\N{\fs38}I mean, I'd watch it, Morty, for at least 11 minutes a pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定还能有分镜脚本\N{\fs38}You know, may-maybe they'll do it board-driven.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个想法很令人欣慰啊 Rick\N{\fs38}You know, that's a real comforting idea, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.11,0:20:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道什么呢 Morty\N{\fs38}What do you know, Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又知道啥呢\N{\fs38}What do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.91,0:21:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 大家好\N{\fs38}Hi, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是你们恐怖课的新老师\N{\fs38}I'm your new teacher for scary class.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫恐怖Johnson\N{\fs38}My name is Scary Mr. Johnson.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.08,0:21:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实吧\N{\fs38}Uh, actually, you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.35,0:21:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我爸的名字 你们干脆叫我恐怖Glenn好了\N{\fs38}That's my dad's name, so why don't you just call me Scary Glenn, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你们之前的老师\N{\fs38}So, anyway, I understand your previous teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.31,0:21:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们学恐怖基本原理\N{\fs38}was having you work on fundamentals of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.15,0:21:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是啥玩意儿啊\N{\fs38}Which is... what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我说的话\N{\fs38}You know? So, uh, here here's what I say
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.91,0:21:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啥也学不会\N{\fs38}you can't learn anything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.12,0:21:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你学会放松\N{\fs38}until you learn... how to chill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才叫做梦嘛 贱人\N{\fs38}This is how you dream, bitch.
